<view class="page merchant-album-page case-draft page-content">
  <block wx:if="{{status === 'loading'}}">
    <ui-skeleton rows="{{5}}" title="{{true}}" />
  </block>

  <block wx:elif="{{status === 'error'}}">
    <ui-empty title="无法加载案例预览" description="{{errorMessage}}" actionText="重试" bind:action="onRetry" />
  </block>

  <block wx:else>
    <view class="case-draft__toolbar" wx:if="{{editable}}">
      <ui-button
        type="secondary"
        size="sm"
        loading="{{polishing}}"
        bind:btntap="onAiPolish"
      >AI 润色</ui-button>
    </view>

    <ui-compliance-notice type="displayDisclaimer" />

    <ui-card shadow="{{true}}" padding="{{true}}">
      <text class="text-h3">{{fromComplete ? '案例预览（确认后完工）' : '公开案例稿'}}</text>
      <text class="text-caption text-secondary case-draft__hint">
        默认按相册节点文字与配图拼成预览，不自动调用大模型。点右上角「AI 润色」可润色正文；配图绑定不变。确认后的文案即上网真源，车主只读。
      </text>
      <text class="text-caption case-draft__label">标题</text>
      <input
        class="case-draft__input"
        value="{{title}}"
        disabled="{{!editable}}"
        maxlength="80"
        bindinput="onTitleInput"
        placeholder="地域｜车型｜项目"
      />
      <text class="text-caption case-draft__label">案例摘要（规则自动拼接 · 页内与搜索共用）</text>
      <textarea
        class="case-draft__textarea case-draft__summary"
        value="{{caseSummary}}"
        disabled="{{!editable}}"
        maxlength="250"
        auto-height
        bindinput="onSummaryInput"
        placeholder="由章节自动拼接；点「AI 润色」会用摘要专用提示词润色。勿写金额。"
      />
      <text class="text-caption text-secondary case-draft__mask-tip">当前配图为原图预览，正式发布时需脱敏。搜索描述由本摘要自动截取，无需另填。</text>
    </ui-card>

    <ui-card
      wx:for="{{sections}}"
      wx:key="key"
      shadow="{{true}}"
      padding="{{true}}"
      class="case-draft__section"
    >
      <text class="text-body case-draft__section-title">{{item.title}}</text>
      <textarea
        class="case-draft__textarea"
        value="{{item.body}}"
        disabled="{{!editable}}"
        maxlength="600"
        auto-height
        data-key="{{item.key}}"
        bindinput="onSectionInput"
        placeholder="根据节点备注生成，可修订；勿写金额"
      />
      <view class="case-draft__section-media">
        <block wx:for="{{media}}" wx:for-item="m" wx:for-index="mi" wx:key="mi">
          <view
            class="case-draft__media-item"
            wx:if="{{m.sectionKey === item.key}}"
          >
            <image class="case-draft__thumb" src="{{m.displayUrl}}" mode="aspectFill" />
            <text class="text-caption">{{m.caption || m.nodeId}}</text>
            <ui-button
              wx:if="{{editable}}"
              type="ghost"
              size="sm"
              data-node-id="{{m.nodeId}}"
              data-idx="{{m.idx}}"
              bind:btntap="onRemoveMedia"
            >移除</ui-button>
          </view>
        </block>
      </view>
    </ui-card>

    <ui-card shadow="{{true}}" padding="{{true}}" wx:if="{{media.length}}">
      <text class="text-h3">全部配图</text>
      <text class="text-caption text-secondary">以下为原图便于核对；确认完工后系统脱敏，车主与正式公示只看脱敏图。</text>
      <view class="case-draft__media">
        <view
          class="case-draft__media-item"
          wx:for="{{media}}"
          wx:for-item="item"
          wx:for-index="mIndex"
          wx:key="mIndex"
        >
          <image class="case-draft__thumb" src="{{item.displayUrl}}" mode="aspectFill" />
          <text class="text-caption">{{item.caption || item.nodeId}} · {{item.sectionKey}}</text>
          <ui-button
            wx:if="{{editable}}"
            type="ghost"
            size="sm"
            data-node-id="{{item.nodeId}}"
            data-idx="{{item.idx}}"
            bind:btntap="onRemoveMedia"
          >移除</ui-button>
        </view>
      </view>
    </ui-card>
    <ui-card shadow="{{true}}" padding="{{true}}" wx:else>
      <text class="text-caption text-secondary">暂无公开配图。请在相册中将过程图设为可公示，或完工脱敏后再嵌入。</text>
    </ui-card>

    <view class="case-draft__actions">
      <ui-button type="secondary" block bind:btntap="onCopyExport">复制文案</ui-button>
      <ui-button wx:if="{{editable}}" type="secondary" block loading="{{saving}}" bind:btntap="onSaveDraft">保存草稿</ui-button>
      <ui-button
        wx:if="{{editable && fromComplete}}"
        type="primary"
        block
        loading="{{completing}}"
        bind:btntap="onConfirmAndComplete"
      >确认并完工</ui-button>
      <ui-button
        wx:elif="{{editable}}"
        type="primary"
        block
        loading="{{saving}}"
        bind:btntap="onConfirmDraft"
      >确认案例稿</ui-button>
    </view>
  </block>
</view>
